cello.alt.servlet.script
Class MultiResourceScript

java.lang.Object
  cello.alt.servlet.script.MultiResourceScript
All Implemented Interfaces:
JavaScript
public class MultiResourceScript
extends java.lang.Object
implements JavaScript

This class is a pseudo-script. It pretends to be a script that requires all scripts in its module, and is used when you write require('module.*').

Author:
Marcello
